<h2>
    Play Blackjack
</h2>
<p>
    Is this your first time?<br>
    If so <a href="{{ app.request.getBaseURL() }}/game/doc">press this link</a> and then come back after reading the rules
</p>
<h3>
    Ready?
</h3>
<form method="post">
    <p>
        Please select how many players you wish to play as:
    </p>
    <input type="number" name="amount" min="1" max="4" value="1" />
    <p>
        If you are ready to play the game, then please press the button bellow
    </p>
    <input type="submit" name="start" value="Start" />
</form>